- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recordings and signal inputs.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new strategy based on convolutional neural networks for ASR performance prediction.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with machine learning techniques for ASR performance prediction.
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is a possible category as the paper deals with signal inputs and ASR performance prediction.
